metadata.name: Pride Perserveres
metadata.description:
A collaboration between Petra, ChloeTheDev, and BruceTheGoose; in commemoration of the first annual Metaverse Pride Parade on 6/27/2020.
This artwork was created by several of the artist's featured in the debut event (and was actually created DURING Nifty Pride 2020!) Sales (and royalties) of this NFT will directly support the Nifty Pride Foundation. Edition of 5
